oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.audit.model.utility
Class AuditAttributeInfo

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.audit.model.utility.AuditAttributeInfo

public class AuditAttributeInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to hold attribute definition and its value for attributes of View object. This class overrides equals method to compare if two AuditAttributeInfo instances are same by comparing attribute name and its value.
